OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA dry day with any early
OL,6,Fcloud clearing to give plenty of sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Becoming warm or very warm,
OL,8,Fespecially away from southern coasts.
OL,9,FLight winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FWarm or
OL,12,Fvery warm during this period, perhaps
OL,13,Fhot, with sunny spells. Mostly dry,
OL,14,Fbut risk of heavy thundery showers on
OL,15,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
